{
  "title": "Dark Velvety Algerian Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A rich and flavorful Algerian dish featuring lamb, fresh thyme, and a hint of mustard, perfect for a midnight craving. This tagine is made with a pressure cooker for a velvety texture.",
